\f6\b food
\f5\b0 .\'a0All 
\f6\b food
\f5\b0  is clean,\'a0but it is wrong for a person to eat anything that causes someone else to stumble.\
\
\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 21\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub It is better not to 
\f6\b eat meat
\f5\b0  or 
\f6\b drink wine
\f5\b0  or to do anything else that will cause your brother or sister to fall.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re 21 verses in and this is the first mention of wine but we\'92ve been talking about food the whole time.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That\'92s important!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because there are denominations and certain churches that LOVE to throw this verse out like it\'92s a life raft to their theology for all things they are uncomfortable with like alcohol all the while they\'92re ignoring the VERY OBVIOUS point of the passage of food because they love their potlucks and their ribs and their steaks.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They ignore the obvious conclusion that Paul is making that what we EAT can cause others to stumble and at the very end he throws wine in also and that is all they see.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s hypocrisy!  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
