\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul doesn\'92t say there is a right or wrong here\'85he leaves it up to the person about what is right or wrong.\
