\ls12\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you have a problem with wine because it might cause someone to stumble and then you better have a problem with eating a steak because I know there are people in this town who are vegetarians who have a problem with that too.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
